hey there i'm karen chu

with you on attending your first coupon

schedule page on the event website to
build out your schedule for each day
i recommend filtering the sessions by
tracks or by content experience level
number two obviously networking is going
to be a little different this time
around
but as a general rule don't just start
with hello and wait for a response
before you say anything more
just go ahead and jump straight into
what you're looking for and provide as
much context as you can early on to help
save time for both parties involved
number three since this is your first
time at the event i recommend checking
out the 101 track
this track has been especially curated
for newcomers like yourself
and there are sessions on all three days
of the event and if you're looking to
get more situated with the community
you can also check out the community
track and with that i hope you find
these pointers helpful and i will see
